            // DialogueEvent
            // 不错嘛。看来你一路打到了最后。
            AddTranslation("Well that was neat. I see you've made it all the way to the end.", "善哉，汝竟行至其终矣。");
            // 我猜你肯定在期待什么最终决战吧。
            AddTranslation("I bet you think there's going to be some sort of final boss fight.", "汝必谓将有终竟易魁之战。");
            // 但那个蠢[c:bR]模组作者[c:]还没做到那一步呢！
            AddTranslation("But that stupid [c:bR]modder[c:] hasn't gotten around to it yet!", "然彼愚[c:bR]补缀者[c:]尚未及此！");
            // 所以呢，我只能这样……
            AddTranslation("So instead, I'm just going to have to do this…", "故我惟得为此……");
            // 运气真背啊伙计。
