            // 那个档案保管员女士……乍看挺和善，但你不觉得她有点阴…阴森吗？
            AddTranslation("That Archivist lady... She seems real nice at first but, isn't there something a little sinister about her?", "彼典牍之妇……初见若善，然汝不觉其稍阴……阴乎？");
            // 跟格…格里魔拉比差远了，实话告诉你。
            AddTranslation("Nowhere near as nice as G- Grimora was, I'll tell you that much.", "其善远不及格……格里魔拉，此我可明告汝。");
            // 但索耶……那可怜虫被她虚…虚伪的客套话给骗了。
            AddTranslation("But Sawyer... The p-poor guy's gotten wrapped up under her false p-pleasantries.", "然索耶……彼可怜人，为其伪……伪和所惑矣。");
            // 能试着劝劝他吗？我…我…我说的话他根本不听...
            AddTranslation("Think you could try convincing him out of it? H-H-He won't hear it from me...", "汝能试解之乎？我……我……我之言，彼终不听……");
            // 要不去她墓…墓…墓穴里找那些图书管理员谈谈？
            AddTranslation("Maybe try talking to those Librarians in her c-c-c-crypt?", "盍试与其冢……冢……冢中守牍者言乎？");
            // 噢，太…太好了！你把他救出来了！
            AddTranslation("Oh, G-good! You got him out of there!", "噫，善……善矣！汝出彼于其间矣！");
            // 真希望能拿点东西谢…谢谢你。不过你已经拿到报酬了。
            AddTranslation("I wish I had something to t-t-thank you. But you've gotten your reward already.", "我愿有物以谢……谢汝。然汝既得其报矣。");
            // 谢了老兄！我刚才可担心死他了。
            AddTranslation("Thanks again, dude! I was worried about him.", "复谢矣，友！我方甚忧彼。");
            // 噢，老…老…老…天……出…出…出大事了，对吧？
            AddTranslation("Oh, G-G-G-god... Something terrible h-h-h-happened, didn't it?", "噫，天……天……天……大祸作……作……作矣，然乎？");
            // 我得赶紧撤……
            AddTranslation("I've gotta go...", "我当亟去……");
            // 你…你…你…你还没完成他们的任务？
            AddTranslation("Y-y-y-ou still haven't finished their task?", "汝……汝……汝……汝犹未竟彼辈之事乎？");
            // 要是你能搞定，我可以把文件带回去给他们
            AddTranslation("If you can finish it, I can take the paperwork back to them.", "若汝能竟之，我可持文返与彼辈。");
            // 你…你…你…你把文件搞定了？
            AddTranslation("Y-y-y-ou finished the paperwork?", "汝……汝……汝……汝竟其文矣乎？");
            // 我…我可以送过去，但…但得花点时间
            AddTranslation("I can take it to th-them, but it'll take me a while.", "我……我可持以与彼，然……然须少时。");
            // 我去送文件的时候你去打…打…打一局……
            AddTranslation("G-g-go fight a battle while I deliver these papers...", "我去致文时，汝往战……战……战一局……");
            // 谢…谢…谢了老兄！我把朋友从那些怪胎手里救回来了。
            AddTranslation("Th-th-thanks dude! I got my friend back from those creeps.", "谢……谢……谢矣，友！我已夺我友于彼怪人之手。");
            // 不过他好像有点躁动不安——你能带上他一起走吗？
            AddTranslation("He seems kind of restless though - do you think you can take him with you?", "然彼似稍躁——汝能携彼偕行乎？");
            // 嘘——安静点。
            AddTranslation("Shhhhh - be quiet.", "嘘——毋哗。");
            // 没事别在这瞎晃。
            AddTranslation("If you have no business here, leave us alone.", "若无事于此，则舍我等。");
            // 你想把你的朋友要回去？
            AddTranslation("You wish to have back your friend?", "汝欲复得汝友乎？");
            // 哎呀，但它已经成了我们的心头好。
            AddTranslation("Oh but he's grown so dear to us.", "噫，然彼于我等已甚亲矣。");
            // 就像家人一样。
            AddTranslation("A part of the family.", "若家人然。");
            // 我们真的很在乎它。
            AddTranslation("Truly we do care for him.", "我等诚爱彼。");
            // 不行，我们可不能就这么把它交给你。
            AddTranslation("No, no we won't just give you him.", "不可，不可，我等不徒以彼与汝。");
            // 除非……你能给我们点什么？
            AddTranslation("Unless... You give something to us?", "除非……汝能有所与我等乎？");
            // 除非……你愿意帮我们做点事？
            AddTranslation("Unless... You do something for us?", "除非……汝愿为我等效一事乎？");
            // 对，对。把这些文件拿走。
            AddTranslation("Yes. Yes. Take these files.", "然，然。取此诸牍。");
            // 带着它们去[c:bR]战斗[c:]。把它们整理归档。[c:bR]按顺序[c:]。
            AddTranslation("Take them to [c:bR]battle[c:]. File them together. [c:bR]In order[c:].", "携之往[c:bR]战[c:]。并而归牍之。[c:bR]依次[c:]。");
            // 然后[c:bR]全部盖章[c:]再带回来。
            AddTranslation("Then [c:bR]stamp them all[c:] and bring them back.", "而后[c:bR]尽钤之[c:]，复持以来。");
            // 刚你卡了？
            AddTranslation("Did we lag?", "吾等方滞乎？");
            // 先把文件[c:bR]按顺序[c:]排好，再[c:bR]盖章[c:]，然后带回来。
            AddTranslation("File them [c:bR]in order[c:] then [c:bR]stamp them[c:] and bring them back.", "先依[c:bR]次[c:]归牍之，次[c:bR]钤之[c:]，而后持归。");
            // 看来你不太擅长按指示行事。
            AddTranslation("You seem to struggle with following instructions.", "观汝不善循指。");
            // 你的朋友就归我们了。
            AddTranslation("We shall keep your friend.", "汝友我等留之。");
            // 永远……
            AddTranslation("Forever...", "永矣……");
            // 干得漂亮！
            AddTranslation("You've done it!", "汝竟之矣！");
            // 不错。不错。
            AddTranslation("Good. Good.", "善。善。");
            // 给。拿着。
            AddTranslation("Here. Take it.", "与。取之。");
            // 我们现在用不着它了。
            AddTranslation("We have no use for it now.", "今我等不用之矣。");
            // 现在别来烦我们。
            AddTranslation("Now leave us alone.", "今毋扰我等。");
            // 来得正好。是个挑战者。
            AddTranslation("Just who I needed to see. A challenger.", "吾所欲见者适至矣。角者也。");
            // 最近没啥收获，没毛皮可卖给你……
            AddTranslation("I haven't pelts to sell ye, catchings have been slim...", "近所获寡，无皮可鬻汝……");
            // 毛皮商她……对此不太满意。
            AddTranslation("The Trader... She's not happy with it.", "彼易皮者……不以此为喜。");
            // 这样，你帮我个忙，我也帮你个忙。
            AddTranslation("Say, scratch my back here, and I will scratch yours.", "然则汝助我，我亦助汝。");
            // 再跟我聊聊，保证让你不虚此行。
            AddTranslation("Talk to me again, and I'll make it worth your while.", "更与我言，我必不使汝虚行。");
            // 好！欢迎入伙。
            AddTranslation("Good! Glad t' have ye on th' team.", "善！幸汝入此伍。");
            // 我在附近设了些全息陷阱。帮我逮住它们，有赏。
            AddTranslation("I have some holo-traps set around 'ere. Catch 'em for me and I'll get ye yer prize.", "我于此间设数幻阱。为我执之，则以赏与汝。");
            // 这附近还藏着些陷阱……
            AddTranslation("There are still some traps around 'ere somewhere...", "此间犹有数阱藏焉……");
            // 上好的毛皮。毛皮商见了准高兴。
            AddTranslation("Magnificent pelts. The Trader will be happy to see them.", "善皮也。彼易皮者见之必喜。");
            // 我得去别处下套了。多谢您嘞。
            AddTranslation("I'll take me leave to set my traps elsewhere. Ye have my thanks.", "我当往他处设阱矣。谢汝。");
            // 你连张毛皮都没有……
            AddTranslation("You have no pelts...", "汝无皮……");
            // 等有了再来吧
            AddTranslation("Come back when you have some", "有之而后复来。");
            // 这毛皮不错。我买了。
            AddTranslation("That is a fine pelt. I will buy it from you.", "此皮善矣。我当市之于汝。");
            // 这可是[c:bR]极品[c:]毛皮。我有个特别交易要跟你谈。
            AddTranslation("That is an [c:bR]exceptional[c:] pelt. I have a special trade for you.", "此乃[c:bR]上异[c:]之皮。吾有异易与汝。");
            // 哎。看来有人把这玩意儿的设置给搞砸了。
            AddTranslation("Woof. Apparently somebody screwed with the settings on this thing.", "唉。似有人败乱此物之设矣。");
            // 现在它没法覆盖整张地图了。
            AddTranslation("It can't reach all of the map right now.", "今其未能尽及全图。");
            // 你先去干个BOSS啥的，我这边修着。
            AddTranslation("Go beat a boss or something while I work on this.", "我治此之时，汝且往败一魁之类。");
            // 说真的；这得花点时间。你先去玩会儿游戏，过会儿再来
            AddTranslation("Seriously; it's going to take a while. Just play the game and come back later", "诚言之，此须少时。且行其戏，后复来。");
            // 修是修好了点，但还没法到处跑。
            AddTranslation("It's partially fixed, but it still can't go everywhere.", "虽已小治，犹未能尽至诸处。");
            // 喂，规矩又不是我定的。本来就这样。
            AddTranslation("Hey, I don't make the rules. This is just how it works.", "喂，律非我立。其势本然。");
            // 继续玩下去地图会解锁更多区域。
            AddTranslation("Keep playing and more of the map will open up.", "且续其戏，则图中更多境将启。");
            // 还需要点时间。接着玩就对了。
            AddTranslation("It's going to take more time. Just keep playing.", "犹须更久。且续其戏。");
            // 搞定。现在能用了。
            AddTranslation("There you go. It's working now.", "既矣。今可用矣。");
            // 我得歇会儿……
            AddTranslation("I need a break...", "我须少息……");
            // 你有权保持沉默！
            AddTranslation("You have the right to remain silent!", "汝得缄口！");
            // 这里是[c:bR][v:0][c:]，你被捕了！
            AddTranslation("This is [c:bR][v:0][c:] and you are under arrest!", "此乃[c:bR][v:0][c:]，汝见执矣！");
            // [c:bR][v:0][c:]在此！这次你休想逃走！
            AddTranslation("[c:bR][v:0][c:] here! You're not gettin' away this time!", "[c:bR][v:0][c:]在此！今汝无由得逸！");
            // 死活不论，你都得跟我走！
            AddTranslation("Dead or alive, you're coming with me!", "死生无论，汝皆当从我！");
            // 上次能赢你，这次照样能赢！
            AddTranslation("I got you once before, and I can do it again!", "我尝得汝一次，今亦能复然！");
            // 正义终将降临到你头上！
            AddTranslation("Justice will come to you eventually!", "义终将及汝！");
            // 记住[c:bR][v:0][c:]的大名——我还会回来的！
            AddTranslation("Remember the name [c:bR][v:0][c:] - I will be back!", "记[c:bR][v:0][c:]之名——我必复来！");
            // 呃，嗨。我叫[c:bR][v:0][c:]。
            AddTranslation("Oh, uh, hi there. My name's [c:bR][v:0][c:].", "呃，安。吾名[c:bR][v:0][c:]。");
            // 我是不是该取你首级来着？还是别的啥？
            AddTranslation("I think I'm supposed to take your scalp, or something like that?", "我意当取汝首皮，抑或类此乎？");
            // 你要能当场暴毙就省事儿多了。
            AddTranslation("If you could just die right here that would make things so much easier for me.", "汝若即死于此，则我事省矣。");
            // 没错，又是我，[c:bR][v:0][c:]
            AddTranslation("Yeah, it's me, [c:bR][v:0][c:]. Again.", "然，复是我，[c:bR][v:0][c:]。");
            // 这次能不能给我省点事儿？
            AddTranslation("Do you think you could make this easier for me this time?", "今能少省我力乎？");
            // 哟，是你啊。上次不是把你干掉了吗？
            AddTranslation("Oh it's you. Didn't I kill you last time?", "噫，是汝。上次非已杀汝乎？");
            // 又回来了？我还得再干你一次？
            AddTranslation("And you're back? I have to do this all over again?", "又返乎？我复须尽为之乎？");
            // 这破工作我真是干够了。
            AddTranslation("I'm not sure I like this job.", "我未必喜此役也。");
            // 哦，见鬼。
            AddTranslation("Oh. Dang it.", "噫。可恶。");
            // 呃，这就有点尴尬了。
            AddTranslation("Well, this is embarrassing.", "然则，此诚可愧。");
            // 看来我得改天再来了。当赏金猎人真够怪的。
            AddTranslation("I guess I'll be back later, or something. Being a bounty hunter is weird.", "我意后当复来云尔。为购捕者，诚怪也。");
            // 这具容器是[c:bR][v:0][c:]。
            AddTranslation("This vessel is [c:bR][v:0][c:].", "此皿乃[c:bR][v:0][c:]。");
            // 听我号令，他会把你的头皮从脑袋上剥下来。
            AddTranslation("By my command, he will separate your scalp from your head.", "承我命，彼将剥汝首皮。");
            // 为什么？
            AddTranslation("Why?", "何也？");
            // 我的动机岂是你能理解的。
            AddTranslation("My motivations are beyond your understanding.", "我之意，非汝所能知。");
            // 我已修复名为[c:bR][v:0][c:]的容器。
            AddTranslation("I have restored the vessel named [c:bR][v:0][c:].", "我已复名为[c:bR][v:0][c:]之皿。");
            // 这次你可没上次那么走运能逃掉了。
            AddTranslation("You shall not be so fortunate as to escape this time.", "今汝不复得若前之幸而逸矣。");
            // 在名为[c:bR][v:0][c:]的容器面前颤抖吧
            AddTranslation("Cower in fear before the vessel named [c:bR][v:0][c:]", "于名为[c:bR][v:0][c:]之皿前慑伏。");
            // 记住失败的痛苦吧，准备好下次继续享受它。
            AddTranslation("Remember the pain of defeat and prepare to feel it once more.", "志败之痛，而备复受之。");
            // 心有余而力不足。
            AddTranslation("The spirit is willing but the steel is weak.", "志虽可，而钢弱。");
            // 下次我不会再犯同样的错误。
            AddTranslation("I will not make the same mistake next time.", "后不复蹈此失。");
            // 差不多得了。
            AddTranslation("That's quite enough of that.", "足矣。");
            // 现在它已经内置了[c:g1]宝[c:][c:g2]石[c:][c:g3]系[c:][c:g1]统[c:]
            AddTranslation("Now it has [c:g1]g[c:][c:g2]e[c:][c:g3]m[c:][c:g1]s[c:] built right in", "今其中已内具[c:g1]玉[c:][c:g2]系[c:][c:g3]之[c:][c:g1]机[c:]。");
            // 啥？你的卡牌全都宝石化了？
            AddTranslation("What? All of your cards are already gemified?", "何？汝诸牌皆已玉化乎？");
            // 这倒有点意思。
            AddTranslation("That's almost impressive.", "此几可观矣。");
            // 那你就随便选个宝石印记加上吧。
            AddTranslation("I guess I'll let you pick a mox sigil to add instead.", "然则听汝择一玛珂印而益之。");
            // 看来你的卡牌都宝石化了，那就选个宝石印记加上去得了。
            AddTranslation("Looks like all your cards are gemified, so pick a mox sigil to add instead.", "观汝诸牌皆已玉化，则择一玛珂印而益之。");
            // 哈？你所有卡牌都已经外骨骼超频了？
            AddTranslation("What? All of your cards are already skeleclocked?", "何？汝诸牌皆已骨机化乎？");
            // 你对这种平庸升级的执着真是令人叹服。
            AddTranslation("You are incredibly dedicated to this mediocre upgrade.", "汝于此庸升之专，诚可异也。");
            // 看来你只能从这些里面挑一张了。
            AddTranslation("I guess you'll have to choose one of these instead.", "然则汝惟得择此中之一。");
            // 还是没得升级？那就从这些里面选吧。
            AddTranslation("Still nothing to upgrade? Pick one of these.", "犹无可升乎？择此中之一。");

            // DialogueState
            // 太简单了……
            AddTranslation("TOO EASY...", "太易矣……");
            // 继续啊……
            AddTranslation("KEEP GOING...", "且续之……");
            // 有点意思……
            AddTranslation("IMPRESSIVE...", "稍可观矣……");
            // 他们认输了？
            AddTranslation("DO THEY GIVE UP?", "彼辈屈乎？");
            // 确实认输了
            AddTranslation("THEY DO GIVE UP", "彼辈果屈矣");
            // 牌组太小了
            AddTranslation("ITS TOO SMALL", "牌列太小矣");
            // 大小刚好
            AddTranslation("ITS JUST RIGHT", "其大适矣");
            // 嘘——过来这边
            AddTranslation("SSH - COME OVER HERE", "嘘——来此。");
            // 咱们开始吧
            AddTranslation("LETS DO THIS", "其为之。");
            // 嘘——把东西拿来
            AddTranslation("SSH - BRING IT HERE", "嘘——持物来此。");
            // 东西去哪了？
            AddTranslation("WHERE DID IT GO?", "物安在？");
            // 施舍点钱呗？
            AddTranslation("SPARE SOME CASH?", "可施些财乎？");
            // 谢了！
            AddTranslation("THANK YOU!", "谢矣！");
            // 让我看看你的实力
            AddTranslation("SHOW ME POWER", "示我以威。");
            // 我爱骨头！！
            AddTranslation("I LOVE BONES!!", "我爱骨！！");
            // 我爱骨头！！！！
            AddTranslation("I LOVE BONES!!!!", "我爱骨！！！！");
            // 来搞点科学
            AddTranslation("LETS DO SCIENCE", "其试理矣。");
            // 你把它弄坏了？！
            AddTranslation("YOU BROKE IT?!", "汝坏之乎？！");
            // 科学的胜利
            AddTranslation("A WIN FOR SCIENCE", "理之胜也");
            // 在找工作吗？
            AddTranslation("LOOKING FOR A JOB?", "求事乎？");
            // 滚回去干活
            AddTranslation("GET BACK TO WORK", "归而作事");
            // 你把它搞坏了？！
            AddTranslation("YOU BROKE IT?!", "汝坏之乎？！");
            // 这是你的报酬
            AddTranslation("HERE'S YOUR PAYMENT", "此汝之酬也");
            // 我朋友不见了
            AddTranslation("MY FRIEND IS LOST", "我友亡矣");
            // 你找到他了！
            AddTranslation("YOU FOUND HIM!", "汝得彼矣！");
            // 金子！
            AddTranslation("GOLD!", "金！");
            // 没金子？
            AddTranslation("NO GOLD?", "无金乎？");
            // 金子！！！
            AddTranslation("GOLD!!!", "金！！！");
            // 救命！
            AddTranslation("HELP!", "救我！");
            // 糟了……
            AddTranslation("OH NO...", "噫，不可……");
            // 呼！
            AddTranslation("PHEW!", "呼！");
            // 烧啊宝贝烧
            AddTranslation("BURN BABY BURN", "焚矣，友，焚矣");
            // 太解压了……
            AddTranslation("SO SATISFYING...", "快甚……");
            // 传送带实战测试
            AddTranslation("CONVEYOR FIELD TRIALS", "输带实斗之试");
            // 开始实战测试？
            AddTranslation("START FIELD TRIALS?", "始实斗之试乎？");
            // 实战测试进行中
            AddTranslation("FIELD TRIALS IN PROGRESS", "实斗之试方行");
            // 实战测试完成
            AddTranslation("FIELD TRIALS COMPLETE", "实斗之试已竟");
            // 轰轰轰
            AddTranslation("BOOM BOOM BOOM", "轰轰轰");
            // 咱们炸了它
            AddTranslation("LET'S BLOW IT UP", "其爆之");
            // 保持爆炸输出
            AddTranslation("KEEP UP THE BOOM", "续其轰");
            // 真爆啊
            AddTranslation("TRULY EXPLOSIVE", "诚爆矣");
            // 去抓个逃犯？
            AddTranslation("CATCH A FUGITIVE?", "执一逃者乎？");
            // 咱们去抓逃犯？！
            AddTranslation("LET'S CATCH A FUGITIVE?!", "其执逃者乎？！");
            // 逮住他！
            AddTranslation("LET'S GET HIM!", "执彼！");
            // 抓到啦！
            AddTranslation("YOU GOT HIM!", "得彼矣！");
            // 真扫兴
            AddTranslation("DISAPPOINTING", "扫兴甚矣");
            // 太棒了
            AddTranslation("ITS GLORIOUS", "美矣");
            // 要抓个逃犯？
            AddTranslation("CATCH A FUGITIVE?", "执一逃者乎？");
            // 咱们去抓逃犯？！
            AddTranslation("LET'S CATCH A FUGITIVE?!", "其执逃者乎？！");
            // 逮住他！
            AddTranslation("LET'S GET HIM!", "执彼！");
            // 抓到啦！
            AddTranslation("YOU GOT HIM!", "得彼矣！");
            // 真扫兴
            AddTranslation("DISAPPOINTING", "扫兴甚矣");
            // 太棒了
            AddTranslation("ITS GLORIOUS", "美矣");
            // 喂伙计
            AddTranslation("OY MATEY", "喂，友");
            // 来战个痛快
            AddTranslation("LET'S FIGHT", "其战矣");
            // 打得不错
