            AddTranslation("A simple invertebrate, with barbed tentacles capable of paralyzing the biggest of creatures.", "一无脊之物也，而其刺触足痹至巨之物。");
            // 跳鼠
            AddTranslation("Jerboa", "跳鼠");
            // 这只瘦小的啮齿动物——灵敏的跳鼠，会在场地中毫无顾忌地四处跳跃。
            AddTranslation("A meager rodent, the jumpy Jerboa will carelessly leap throughout the board.", "小鼠也，跳鼠轻率，遍跃于局。");
            // 中国僵尸
            AddTranslation("Jiangshi", "僵尸");
