            AddTranslation("emerging from the winter forests, the hateful krampus marches through, carrying unfortunate souls in his sack.", "出于冬林，憎者坎卜斯行而过，负不幸之魂于囊。");
            // 裂口女
            AddTranslation("Kuchisake-onna", "裂口女");
            // 她究竟在面具之下藏着什么？
